Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited Key Developments

Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited, Board Meeting, May 17, 2017
May 18 17
Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited, Board Meeting, May 17, 2017. Agenda: To approve the additional sale of 40,248,000 Class B shares in Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited, owned by The National Gas Company of Trinidad and Tobago Limited.


Trinidad and Tobago NGL Mulls Acquisitions
May 18 17
Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited (TTSE:NGL) is seeking acquisitions. Trinidad and Tobago NGL, said, “The management outlined a host of initiatives product trading, commodity trading, marketing initiatives, and were also looking at a couple possible acquisitions as well, which would only further enhance the performance of the organization.”


Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited Announces Audited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended December 31, 2016
Mar 29 17
Trinidad and Tobago NGL Limited announced audited consolidated earnings results for the year ended December 31, 2016. For the year, the company reported total income of TTD 164,174,000 against TTD 136,279,000 a year ago. Profit before income tax was TTD 180,345,000 against TTD 371,137,000 a year ago. Total comprehensive profit was TTD 344,767,000 or TTD 1.16 per basic and diluted share against loss of TTD 402,763,000 or TTD 2.40 per basic and diluted share a year ago. Net cash flow provided by operating activities was TTD 416,905,000 compared to TTD 12,000 a year ago.


